data.description: 1 Story cul-de-sac with an in ground heated pool and hot tub.  Stepping into this home is delight, Beautiful and updated for energy efficiency.  It features new windows with a lifetime transferable warranty throughout the home, new hot water heater, new A/C and furnace. Sellers have put new carpet in bedrooms, new french door in living room, and primary bathroom and closet has been remodeled.  Outdoors has manicured lawn with landscape lighting,  new facia, soffits and gutters. This home has a great back yard area perfect for yourselves or your guests. Pool has waterfall features, new pumps and lighting.  Patio has new additions to add to the usefulness.  It is ready to entertain now!
